metadata.name: Mellow Moment
metadata.description: The secret of change is to focus all of your energy not on fighting the old, but on building the new. After the dust settles you'll find a mellow moment. A moment to let go of the pain. And in that moment we can find the time to  appreciate colors and textures, memories that linger, smells that take you home, & music that will still your aching heart. Love will give you the strength to transform pain into power.
